    <section id="id26998240">
      <title>Memorandum</title>
      <list id="id20685838" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>The wood block has the greatest mass.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id27293187">1. Density = mass per volume. Therefore </para>
      <para id="id26941676">(a) = 1,6 g/cm<sup>3</sup></para>
      <para id="id26248605">(b) = 2,5 g/cm<sup>3</sup></para>
      <para id="id22905461">(c) 8,7 g/cm<sup>3</sup></para>
      <para id="id26974114">(d) = 7,7 g/cm<sup>3</sup></para>
      <para id="id21819829">(e) 0,8 g/cm<sup>3</sup></para>
      <para id="id26953784">2. Use two liquids that do not mix. Pour them in a glass jug. The liquid with the lower density will float on the other, e.g. oil on water.</para>
    </section>
